data.description: Come see this great first time buyer home priced to sell motivated owner. Great home to earn some sweat equity with room to add a 2nd Bathroom and partialy finished three season porch finish and look over your back yard. Great area of South st that you can walk to Bridgewater center with its restaraunts, shopping and churches. Plenty of off street parking with a large beautiful yard for many a cook outs. Close to major highways Rt.24 and Rt.495. Book your appointment to get in on this great deal.
